<dd>36. <a href="/wiki/Samuel_Chase" title="Samuel Chase">Samuel Chase</a></dd>
<dd>37. <a href="/wiki/William_Paca" title="William Paca">William Paca</a></dd>
<dd>38. <a href="/wiki/Thomas_Stone" title="Thomas Stone">Thomas Stone</a></dd>
<dd>39. <a href="/wiki/Charles_Carroll_of_Carrollton" title="Charles Carroll of Carrollton">Charles Carroll of Carrollton</a></dd>
</dl>
</td>
<td style="width: 33.33%;" align="left" valign="top">
<p><a href="/wiki/Virginia" title="Virginia">Virginia</a></p>
